#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kimagemapeditor;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kimagemapeditor;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kimagemapeditor; is a &HTML; imagemap editor developed by the &kde; "
"community. It allows you to create and modify &HTML; <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Imagemap\">Imagemaps.</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"&kimagemapeditor; je &HTML; urejevalnik slikovnih zemljevidov, ki ga je "
"razvila skupnost &kde;. Omogoča ustvarjanje in spreminjanje &HTML; <ulink "
"url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imagemap\">Slikovnih zemljevidov.</ulink>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kimagemapeditor;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kimagemapeditor;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kimagemapeditor; main window."
msgstr "&kimagemapeditor; glavno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A common use case is a world map where each country is an imagemap. By "
"clicking on a country in the map you can open a link to the selected country."
msgstr ""
"Pogost primer uporabe je zemljevid sveta, kjer je vsaka država slikovni "
"zemljevid. S klikom na državo na zemljevidu odprete povezavo do izbrane "
"države."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an imagemap requires the following steps:"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje slikovnega zemljevida zahteva naslednje korake:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Load an image file (<filename class=\"extension\">png</filename>, <filename "
"class=\"extension\">jpg</filename>, <filename class=\"extension\">gif</"
"filename>) or a &HTML; file from your disk or drag it into the image area. "
"Select an image in the <guilabel>Images</guilabel> docker."
msgstr ""
"Naloži slikovno datoteko (<filename class=\"extension\">png</filename>, "
"<filename class=\"extension\">jpg</filename>, <filename class=\"extension"
"\">gif</filename>) ali &HTML; datoteko z diska ali jo povlecite v območje "
"slike. Izberite sliko v doku <guilabel>Slike</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a imagemap using <menuchoice><guimenu>Map</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Map</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu and enter a map name."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte slikovni zemljevid z <menuchoice><guimenu>Zemljevid</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Novi zemljevid</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz menija in "
"vnesite ime zemljevida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu is enabled and you can select the "
"appropriate geometric shape like <guimenuitem>Circle</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Rectangle</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Polygon</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Freehand Polygon</guimenuitem> and define a clickable area in "
"the image."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je meni <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> omogočen in lahko izberete ustrezno "
"geometrijsko obliko, kot je <guimenuitem>Krog</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Pravokotnik</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Poligon</guimenuitem> "
"ali <guimenuitem>Prostoročni mnogokotnik</guimenuitem> in določite območje "
"na sliki, ki ga je mogoče klikniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Area Tag Editor</guilabel> dialog is displayed. On the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab enter the attributes <guilabel>HREF</"
"guilabel> (a link's target &URL;), <guilabel>Alt.Text</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Target</guilabel> and <guilabel>Title</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se pogovorno okno <guilabel>Urejevalnik območnih oznak</guilabel>. "
"Na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> vnesite atribute <guilabel>HREF</"
"guilabel> (cilj povezave &URL;), <guilabel>Alt.Text</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Target (Cilj)</guilabel> in <guilabel>Title (Naslov)</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Coordinates</guilabel> tab shows the geometric data of the "
"shape. Editing the value allows you to adjust size and position on the image "
"as your changes are immediately visible in the image. Size and position can "
"be altered using the mouse as well."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Koordinate</guilabel> prikazuje geometrijske podatke "
"oblike. Urejanje vrednosti vam omogoča prilagajanje velikosti in položaja na "
"sliki, saj so vaše spremembe takoj vidne na sliki. Velikost in položaj lahko "
"spreminjate tudi z miško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open the <guilabel>Area Tag Editor</guilabel> dialog for an already "
"defined imagemap use <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu or the context menu of the region."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti pogovorno okno <guilabel>Urejevalnik območnih oznak</"
"guilabel> za že definiran slikovni zemljevid, uporabite "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu> "
"ali kontekstnem meniju regije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Map</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show HTML</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to view the generated &HTML; code of the map."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Zemljevid</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži HTML</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> za ogled generirane &HTML; kode zemljevida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next open <menuchoice><guimenu>Image</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Usemap...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and enter the map name as usemap value. Save your "
"work with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Open the &HTML; file in &konqueror; to verify "
"that the imagemap is working as expected."
msgstr ""
"Nato odprite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sliko</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uredi "
"zemljevid uporabe...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in vnesite ime zemljevida "
"kot vrednost zemljevida uporabe. Shranite svoje delo z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Odprite &HTML; datoteka v &konqueror; da preverite, ali "
"imagemap deluje po pričakovanjih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuration options of &kimagemapeditor; can be accessed by opening the "
"configuration dialog with selecting <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kimagemapeditor;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from "
"the menu."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti konfiguracije &kimagemapeditor; lahko dostopate tako, da odprete "
"konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno z izbiro <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kimagemapeditor;...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> v meniju."

